transcript:

Executive: Hello.
Customer: Yes.
Executive: Hello, good afternoon sir.
Customer: Hello.

Executive: Sir, abhi aapne call kiya tha na ki aapko issue aa raha tha ki by leads nahi dekh pa rahe aap.
Customer: Haan, wo meet pe kar lete hain, Google meet pe.
Executive: Haan, to sir main aap main apna aapko ek link bhej raha hu meet pe, thik hai sir.
Customer: Join kar lijiye.
Executive: Mail pe bhejiye, haan.
Executive: Haan sir, bhej diya maine. Check kar lijiye sir. Hmm.
Customer: Nahi, kispe bheja hai?
Executive: Sir, tharsole@gmail.com.
Customer: Achha, tharsole pe bheja hai.
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Join kar liya maine Google Meet, call disconnect kar sakte hain.
Executive: Thik hai sir.
